Description:
    Creates a new Angular component

Example:
    yo angular-express:component foo

    Depending on what parts are selected, this will create:
        app/components/foo/foo.js
        app/components/foo/foo.html
        app/components/foo/foo.less
        app/components/foo/foo-controller.js
        app/components/foo/foo-controller_test.js
        app/components/foo/foo-directive.js
        app/components/foo/foo-directive_test.js
        app/components/foo/foo-service.js
        app/components/foo/foo-service_test.js